snippet.title: Save Robbie
snippet.description:
Hi! 

I’m Save Robbie! 

Most of my videos involve humor & I often over exaggerate to get you to laugh. (for entertainment purposes only) I enjoy laughing & don’t take life too seriously. My intentions always come from my heart no matter what mood I’m in. I’m human & vlog a range of my emotions. I’m here to grow & become a better person. On this channel I vlog & have fun. I’m in recovery & this community has been so uplifting. I named my channel “Save Robbie” because vlogging really helps me mentally & spiritually. 

Thanks to all of my loving friends 

My email is: saverobbie.1982@gmail.com (Lokomai helps me with my emails so please be patient)

God bless, Robbie

It is FREE to enter or be a part of my trivia/giveaway’s. I just ask a question and whoever answers it correctly first gets their name entered in the drawing (Make sure you’re on live chat) I draw names for the winners. YouTube is not a sponsor of my contests and is not liable for the contest . See community guidelines
